Interface FieldDecl

All Superinterfaces:
ClassMember, java.lang.Cloneable, Copy, JL, Node, NodeOps, Term
All Known Implementing Classes:
FieldDecl_c
public interface FieldDecl
extends ClassMember

A FieldDecl is an immutable representation of the declaration of a field of a class.
